\f0\fs24 \cf0 The Artisan Legacy\
\
A celebration of India's enduring craftsmanship, thoughtfully curated to honour traditions that have been cherished through generations.\
Housed in a hand-carved wooden keepsake chest adorned with intricate floral motifs, this collection brings together timeless artistry from across India. Every piece has been carefully selected not only for its beauty, but for the story it carries\'97from skilled artisans preserving age-old crafts to the home of someone who values meaningful gifting.\
Designed to be treasured long after the occasion has passed, the keepsake chest becomes a lasting home for jewellery, letters, treasured memories, and cherished heirlooms, making it a beautiful reminder of India's rich artistic heritage.\
\
